---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Our Story — The Anti-Country-Club | Tennis Terminal"
  description="We built the opposite of the country club: a self-serve practice room where anyone can walk in, grab a bay, and just play. Welcoming, tech-forward, affordable."
  path="/about"
>
  <section style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,84px) 24px clamp(24px,4vw,40px);text-align:center">
    <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);margin-bottom:16px">Our story</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(38px,5.4vw,60px);line-height:1.04">The anti-country-club</h1>
  </section>

  <section style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px clamp(40px,6vw,64px)">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,21px);line-height:1.65;color:var(--tt-ink-700);text-wrap:pretty">We got tired of courts you had to join a club to touch, coaches you had to book weeks out, and prices that treated a casual hit like a luxury. So we built the opposite.</p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,21px);line-height:1.65;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:20px;text-wrap:pretty">Tennis Terminal is a self-serve practice room where anyone — beginners, families, rusty former players — can walk in, grab a bay, and just play. No membership to belong to. No one watching. Your court, your schedule.</p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,21px);line-height:1.65;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:20px;text-wrap:pretty">It started with a simple frustration: wanting to hit for an hour after work and finding nowhere in the neighborhood that would just let you. We figured smart locks and app-controlled machines could run a great little court without a front desk — and pass the savings straight to you.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section style="background:var(--tt-white);border-top:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade)">
    <div style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,84px) 24px">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px"><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tt-play-green);margin-bottom:14px">What we're about</div><h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.8vw,40px);line-height:1.08">Three things we won't compromise on</h2></div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:22px">
        <div style="background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:18px;padding:30px"><h3 style="font-size:22px">Welcoming</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:10px">Everyone belongs here — every age, body type and skill level. No dress code, no gatekeeping, no side-eye.</p></div>
        <div style="background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:18px;padding:30px"><h3 style="font-size:22px">Tech-forward</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:10px">The tech does the boring parts — booking, unlocking, feeding balls — so you can just focus on playing.</p></div>
        <div style="background:var(--tt-honey-cream);border:1px solid var(--tt-cream-shade);border-radius:18px;padding:30px"><h3 style="font-size:22px">Affordable</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-ink-700);margin-top:10px">No membership, no coach you're forced to book. Pay for the time you play — that's the whole model.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:var(--tt-court-ink)">
    <div style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(48px,7vw,80px) 24px;text-align:center">
      <div style="width:60px;height:60px;margin:0 auto 24px;position:relative"><div style="width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:50%;background:var(--tt-play-green)"></div><div style="position:absolute;top:-8%;right:-8%;width:38%;height:38%;border-radius:50%;background:var(--tt-ball-yellow);border:4px solid var(--tt-court-ink)"></div></div>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,40px);line-height:1.1;color:var(--tt-honey-cream)">Come play with us</h2>
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--tt-honey-cream);opacity:0.85;margin-top:14px">Join the waitlist and be first through the door on the Brooklyn waterfront.</p>
      <a href="/join" style="display:inline-block;font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:600;font-size:16px;color:var(--tt-court-ink);background:var(--tt-ball-yellow);padding:15px 30px;border-radius:10px;margin-top:26px">Join the waitlist →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
